    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="INTRO-GOOGLE-ANALYTICS-FOR-WORDPRESS-BY-MONSTERINSIGHTS"><a href="#INTRO-GOOGLE-ANALYTICS-FOR-WORDPRESS-BY-MONSTERINSIGHTS" class="headerlink" title="INTRO : GOOGLE ANALYTICS FOR WORDPRESS BY MONSTERINSIGHTS"></a>INTRO : GOOGLE ANALYTICS FOR WORDPRESS BY MONSTERINSIGHTS</h3><span id="more"></span>
<p>這篇介紹GOOGLE ANALYTICS FOR WORDPRESS BY MONSTERINSIGHTS。</p>
<h3 id="Step-by-step"><a href="#Step-by-step" class="headerlink" title="Step by step"></a>Step by step</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.WordPress後台 -&gt; 外掛 -&gt; 搜尋並安裝Google Analytics <span class="keyword">for</span> WordPress by MonsterInsights</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">2.建立Google Analytics帳號</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">3.在Google Analytics管理 -&gt; 建立資源 -&gt; 顯示進階選項 -&gt; 點選&lt;建立通用 Analytics (分析) 資源&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">4.填入網站網址 -&gt; 點選只建立通用 Analytics (分析) 資源</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">5.在WordPress後台 -&gt; 外掛 -&gt; Google Analytics <span class="keyword">for</span> WordPress by MonsterInsights -&gt; Settings -&gt; Connect MonsterInsights -&gt; 完成設定</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
